WEBVTT

00:01.791 --> 00:05.365
It's a big world, full of difference and diversity.

00:07.951 --> 00:11.712
How you see others is influenced by your own cultural perspective...

00:12.765 --> 00:16.284
...and how others see you is influenced by their cultural perspective.

00:18.585 --> 00:19.916
What happens when you speak?

00:20.797 --> 00:24.343
Do people from other cultures understand you in the way you intended?

00:26.485 --> 00:29.027
And what happens with different cultures in the workplace?

00:29.607 --> 00:32.915
How rigid or flexible is their approach to rules?

00:33.665 --> 00:36.213
Is formal or informal behavior expected?

00:37.044 --> 00:39.693
And how do different cultures approach timekeeping?

00:41.973 --> 00:43.669
To be a savvy global traveler,...

00:44.236 --> 00:48.543
...you need to be willing to undertake the journey of understanding other cultures.

01:07.705 --> 01:13.044
Develop cultural intelligence so you can communicate confidently across cultures.

